<h3 id="FT_HAS_FIXED_SIZES">FT_HAS_FIXED_SIZES</h3>
<p>Defined in FT_FREETYPE_H (freetype/freetype.h).</p>
<pre>
#define <b>FT_HAS_FIXED_SIZES</b>( face ) \
