<h4>note</h4>
<p>Use <a href="ft2-base_interface.html#FT_Done_Face">FT_Done_Face</a> to destroy the created <a href="ft2-base_interface.html#FT_Face">FT_Face</a> object (along with its slot and sizes).</p>

